					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12798884#post-4420892</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12798884/scp-4396#post-4420892</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2019 00:26:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>FourMinorSix</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5690407</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It’s a nice little idea and I upvoted either way, but I’d recommend the following fixes:</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Description</span><br /> across the globe <strong>so</strong> as to respond to any reports (correct phrasing)</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Addendum</span><br /> accompanied by <strong>F</strong>oundation staff (capitalisation)</p> <p>The trail <strong>led</strong> him back to his house (spelling)</p> <p>Also, for the son to have regained consciousness, he must have passed out in the first place, so you may want to mention that briefly - “climb out of the wreckage of the vehicle <em>before passing out</em>” perhaps?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
